    "For instance, ChatGPT can provide information and insights to users in various domains such as project management 22, drafting emails 23, or research tasks 24, thereby aiding the user in acquiring knowledge.",
    "Knowledge application, on the other hand, refers to the utilization of the acquired knowledge in relevant situations or tasks 25.",
